# One regex per line. Matches against raw 'SEVERITY|DOMAIN|FINDING|FIX' output.
# Empty lines and lines starting with # are ignored.

# aiostreams_redis hit rate is structurally low (per-user-config cache keys),
# can never reach generic 70% threshold; tracked separately.
\|redis/aiostreams_redis\|hit rate

# authelia_postgres is tiny (~9 MB) — heap_hit doesn't matter on tiny DBs.
\|postgres/authelia_postgres\|

# bitmagnet's unclassified-torrent backlog is being drained by the prune sidecar
# at ~200k/day; the count organically shrinks. Re-enable if it stops shrinking.
\|bitmagnet\|.*unclassified torrents backlog
